#. Tag: title
#: importing-exporting.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting ONIX"
msgstr "Izvoz ONIX"

#. Tag: para
#: importing-exporting.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.editeur.org/onix.html\">ONIX</ulink> is an &XML; "
"format for representing and communicating book industry product information, "
"primarily for book vendors. &appname; can export book collections using a "
"small subset of ONIX."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url = \"http://www.editeur.org/onix.html\"> ONIX </ulink> je &XML; "
"format za predstavljanje i komunikaciju knjizi industriji informacije o "
"proizvodu, prije svega za prodavača knjiga. &appname; može izvoziti zbirke "
"knjiga koristeći mali podskup ONIX."

#. Tag: title
#: importing-exporting.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting Bibtex"
msgstr "Izvoz Bibtex"

#. Tag: para
#: importing-exporting.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When exporting to <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bibtex\">Bibtex</"
"ulink>, the field values may be escaped with braces or quotation marks. If "
"any string macros are used in the collection, they may optionally be "
"exported as macros or expanded. For &URL; fields, &appname; may enclose the "
"field values with the <literal>\\url{...}</literal> tag. Finally, entries "
"with no citation key may be skipped rather than have &appname; auto-generate "
"the key."
msgstr ""
"Kada se izvozi u <ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bibtex\">Bibtex</"
"ulink>, vrijednosti polja se mogu izbjeći vitičastim zagradama ili "
"navodnicima. Ako se neki string makro koristi u kolekciji, oni se opcionalno "
"mogu izvesti kao makroi ili ekspandovati. Za &URL; polja, &appname; mogu "
"uključiti imena polja sa <literal>\\url{...}</literal> oznakom. Konačno, "
"unosi bez bez ključa citata se mogu preskočiti umjesto da imaju &appname; "
"auto-generisani ključ."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: importing-exporting.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Bibtex Export Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Bibtex Opcije Izvoza</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: importing-exporting.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bibtex Export Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Bibtex Opcije Izvoza</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: importing-exporting.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting GCstar"
msgstr "Izvoz GCstar"

#. Tag: para
#: importing-exporting.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application><ulink url=\"http://www.gcstar.org\">GCstar</ulink></"
"application> is another movie collection manager. &appname; is able to "
"export most collection types to a GCstar data file."
msgstr ""
"<application> <ulink url = \"http://www.gcstar.org\"> GCstar </ulink> </"
"application> je još jedan menadžer kolekcija film. &appname; je moći "
"izvoziti većinu tipova kolekciju u datoteku podataka GCstar."

#. Tag: title
#: importing-exporting.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting &XML; via &xslt;"
msgstr "Izvoz &XML; preko &xslt;"

#. Tag: para
#: importing-exporting.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, &appname; is able to process its internal &XML; representation of "
"the collection data through an external &XSL; stylesheet before exporting. "
"This type of export may be useful for generating text reports or other file "
"types."
msgstr ""
"Konačno, &appname; je u mogućnosti da obrađuju svoje unutrašnje &XML; "
"predstavljanje podataka kolekcije kroz vanjski &XSL; stila prije izvoza. Ova "
"vrsta izvoza može biti korisno za generiranje teksta izvještaja ili druge "
"vrste datoteka."

#. Tag: title
#: importing-exporting.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working With Citations"
msgstr "Rad sa Citations"

#. Tag: para
#: importing-exporting.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When working with a <link linkend=\"bibliography\">bibliography</link>, "
"citations for the currently selected entries may be generated and used in "
"various other applications. A citation in bibtex format can be copied to the "
"clipboard, and then pasted in a latex file. Bibtex citations can also be "
"pushed to an external application such as <application>LyX</application> or "
"<application>Kile</application> using the so-called <emphasis><link linkend="
"\"hidden-bibtex-options\">lyxpipe</link></emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Kada radite sa <link linkend = \"Bibliografija\"> Bibliografija </link>, "
"citata za trenutno odabrane stavke mogu nastati i koristiti u raznim drugim "
"aplikacijama. A navođenja u BibTex formatu mogu se kopirati u međuspremnik, "
"a zatim zalijepiti u lateks datoteku. Bibtex citata se također može gurnuti "
"na vanjski program, kao što su <application> Lyx </application> ili "
"<application> Kile </application> pomoću tzv <emphasis> <link linkend = "
"\"skriveni-BibTex-opcije\"> lyxpipe </link> </emphasis>."

